Manual Approval Pipeline Lab

This project demonstrates a simple CI/CD pipeline on AWS with a manual approval stage before production deployment.

Overview

Pipeline flow:

GitHub → AWS CodeBuild → Deploy to Dev (S3) → Manual Approval → Deploy to Prod

Services Used

- AWS CodePipeline
- AWS CodeBuild
- Amazon S3
- Amazon SNS
- AWS IAM
- GitHub

Key Points

- Implemented full CI/CD pipeline
- Added Manual Approval before production
- Used SNS for notifications
- Fixed IAM issue (s3:PutObject AccessDenied)

Files

- index.html
- buildspec.yml

Notes

Practice project demonstrating deployment workflows with approval control.
